# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: Files to KEEP for Docker Build
# These files are needed in Docker image but should be handled carefully:
# - api-keys.json: EXCLUDED from Git (security), but INCLUDED in Docker
# - knowledge_base/ (pre-built database) - KEEP in Git
# - requirements.txt (Python dependencies) - KEEP in Git
# - main.py (inference script) - KEEP in Git
# - inference.sh (entry-point script) - KEEP in Git
